Package: libtap-harness-junit-perl
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${perl:Depends},
 libxml-simple-perl
Description: Generate JUnit compatible output from TAP results
 The only difference between this module and TAP::Harness is that this module
 adds the optional arguments 'xmlfile', 'package', and 'namemangle' that cause
 the output to be formatted into XML in a format similar to the one that is
 produced by the JUnit testing framework.
